SELLERS
-------
git clone https://github.com/commercial-emacs/dignified-elpa.el
make -C dignified-elpa.el install

https://github.com/apps/dignified-elpa -- install for one repo to start.

Create .github/workflows/release.yml in that repo -- decide which
files go into the package.

```
name: Release
on:
  release:
    types: [published]

jobs:
  build:
    uses: commercial-emacs/dignified-elpa/.github/workflows/build.yml@v1
    with:
      files: "your-package.el dir/other.el README"
```

Each tagging of a release publishes to Dignified Elpa.

To sell source code, https://dignified-elpa.commandlinesystems.com/dashboard
and "Complete Stripe".


BUYERS
------
git clone https://github.com/commercial-emacs/dignified-elpa.el
make -C dignified-elpa.el install
Try out any Dignified Elpa package via M-x list-packages.
To purchase source code, M-x dignify.
To see purchases M-x dignified-elpa.
